title: List of New Zealand international footballers born outside New Zealand
text:
This is a list of foreign-born <a href="association%20football">football</a> players who played for the <a href="New%20Zealand%20national%20football%20team">New Zealand national football team</a>.
List by country of birth.
<a href="England">England</a> is the country where most of foreign-born New Zealand players were born.
